~~5 <span class="red">............</span> 5
<span class="red">...........</span> 5 أخ لأم، وأبناء عم <span
~~class="red">...</span> 1 + 2 <span class="red">.....</span> 5 +10 <span
~~class="red">......</span> 15
<span class="red">...........</span> 5 أبنا عم <span
